'CJC-1295 with DAC': ['Studied for longer-lasting stimulation of the growth-hormone/IGF-1 signaling system.','Research interest includes body composition, recovery biology, and sleep-related growth-hormone pulses.','The DAC modification is designed to make the signal last longer in research settings.'],
